<HEADLINE> Huber wins Final Race Before Nagano </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZURICH, Janurary 24 (Xinhua) -- Italy's Guenther Huber boosted
his morale for the Nagano Olympics by winning the final bobsleigh
World Cup two-man event of the season at St. Moritz, Switzerland
on Saturday.
</P>
