Deng Xiaoping Theory to strive for the promotion of reform,
opening-up and modernization and the reunification of the
motherland.
</P>
<P>
With China's reform having entered a crucial stage, the
president said, the CPC is endeavoring to open up a new prospect
for the reform, opening-up and modernization.
</P>
<P>
