an urgent call on Tuesday for more humanitarian aid to people in
Tibet Autonomous Region and Qinghai Province who suffered severe
snowstorms this winter.
</P>
<P>
The donations came from the China Red Cross Foundation plus Red
Cross organizations in the cities of Shanghai, Beijing and
Tianjin, and provinces such as Hainan, Jiling, Hunan and Jiangsu.
</P>
