Tibet and Qinghai in northwest China have been pelted with
almost continuous snowstorms since last September with heavy
losses in human lives and property.
</P>
<P>
The Red Cross organizations and People's Liberation Army troops
have been actively involved in relief work since the disastrous
snowstorms began in the two regions. 
