China Changcheng Construction Corp. has passed the ISO9002 quality
authentication.
</P>
<P>
This brings the total number of the group's leading enterprises
which have passed related quality authentication to 11.
</P>
<P>
The group includes more than 300 enterprises engaged in such
fields as architectural design, science research, construction,
installation and material supply.
</P>
<P>
The corporation has completed buildings with a combined floor
space of more than 60 million square meters since it was set up
more than four decades ago.
</P>
<P>
Over 90 percent of the buildings along the two sides of
Chang'an Avenue and many other famous buildings in Beijing,
including the Great Hall of the People and the Chairman Mao
Memorial Hall, have been built by the corporation.
</P>
<P>
Since 1985 the corporation has won 23 Lu Ban Prizes, the
highest awards in the building sector, and more than 100 quality
prizes given by the state and Beijing Municipal Government.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, the corporation has contracted a large group of
projects in a dozen foreign countries and regions, and it has
established more than 40 joint ventures with its counterparts in
Japan, Singapore and the United States.  
