<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, January 24 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan is considering the
proposals sent by India to operationalize the mechanism of
addressing all the outstanding issues including Kashmir between
the two countries, a Foreign Office spokesman said on Saturday.
