hurdle to the resumption of talks.
</P>
<P>
The resumption of talks between the foreign secretaries of the
two countries depends on when New Delhi comes back to the
situation in last June," when the two foreign secretaries agreed
on a mechanism to address the eight outstanding issues including
Kashmir.
</P>
<P>
