export-oriented production.
</P>
<P>
Those housing and office building projects which are not
directly related to the productive sector and the construction
projects not being implemented yet should not be given priority,
he said.
</P>
<P>
Necessary assistance will be provided to private banks in the
country for their development, while their functions should be
supervised to make sure they conform to the existing laws, rules
and regulations, he said.
