<HEADLINE> Italy to Increase Investment in Bulgaria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, January 23 (Xinhua) -- Italy is interested in the
Bulgaria's light, food processing and textile industries and will
support the establishment of joint ventures, head of an Italian
trade delegation said here Friday.
</P>
<P>
Paolo Lupori, President of the Italian Federation for
Encouraging Export and Import, said agreements have been drafted
on the setting up of joint ventures in Bulgaria.
</P>
<P>
