<HEADLINE> South American Body to Back Blatter for FIFA Post </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, January 23 (Xinhua) -- The South American
Football Association Confederation (CSF) will support
International Football Association Federation (FIFA) General
Secretary Joseph Blatter, if he decides to vie for the presidency
of that organization, according to reports from Asuncion,
Paraguay.
</P>
